id: pm-8myl
title: "Extension install self-copy guard: reject source-inside-destination layouts before fs.cp EINVAL (PM-CLI-28)"
description: "Sentry PM-CLI-28 records a handled production extension/package install reaching node fs.cp with the destination inside the source tree. Detect source/destination identity and containment before copying, return a deterministic actionable pm error, and cover the real install path without suppressing unrelated filesystem failures. Duplicate check: all-status searches for PM-CLI-28, the exact EINVAL title, and self-copy/subdirectory wording found no canonical item; this is related to package-platform maturity and release telemetry."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-07-13T23:35:50.992Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-14T00:29:25.779Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-14T00:29:25.106Z"
author: codex-root
acceptance_criteria: Extension install canonicalizes source and destination parents before containment checks; symlinked or temp-root-contained destinations are staged outside the source without fs.cp self-copy; a filesystem-root source fails before copying with extension_install_source_contains_destination; unrelated filesystem errors remain visible; real-filesystem regressions and packed smoke pass.
parent: pm-ugqx
risk: low
confidence: high
reporter: codex-root
severity: medium
environment: pm-cli 2026.7.13; Node v26.4.0; Linux; live Sentry PM-CLI-28 plus sandboxed real-filesystem reproduction
repro_steps: "Resolve an extension source through a symlink whose canonical destination lies below that source, then install it. Before the fix fs.cp receives a destination inside the source and throws EINVAL."
resolution: Canonical realpath containment now stages extension sources safely outside their destination and returns extension_install_source_contains_destination before unsafe root self-copy.
expected_result: Install stages the source outside its canonical tree or returns a deterministic pm error before copying when no safe staging parent exists.
actual_result: The previous copy path compared lexical paths only and reached node fs.cp self-copy EINVAL for canonical containment layouts.
component: extension and package install copy safety
regression: false
customer_impact: Extension/package installs could fail with a low-level filesystem exception and create high-severity telemetry noise.
